FEATURES of &quot;Firefox&quot;:
----------------------

(1)Comprehensive popup controls to keep unwanted advertising off your desktop;

(2)A tab browsing mode that lets you open several pages in a single window, allowing you to load links in the background without leaving the page you're on;

(3)Integrated search (powered by Google);

(4)Industry leading accessibility with Find As You Type - find links and page   text by simply typing;

(5)Simplified privacy controls that let you cover your tracks more effectively;

(6)A streamlined browser window that lets you see more of the page than any other browser while at the same time being more configurable;

(7)A large variety of free downloadable extensions and themes that add specific functionality and visual changes to the browser.



